{"tid":1605110,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"[香城 Online] 鍵戰部成立新職業 - 易容師！","createTime":"2019-09-30T07:36:43.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-07T16:52:02.000Z","uid":236171,"like":100,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":45,"replies":[{"pid":"8d75f61f9f7dd3ea502319358866713d143db9fd","tid":1605110,"uid":236171,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-30T07:36:43.000Z","msg":"話說而家有好多仆街藍屍 page 會偷拍義士大頭相擺上 page，令義士無論喺法律上定人身安全上都非常不利！<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/irUEgfD.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FirUEgfD.jpg&h=1fcfbeff&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n為咗減低呢個行為對我哋義士造成嘅傷害，我諗到以下呢個方法：<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">就係幫起底相做 Faceswap，<br />\n然後擺翻上藍屍起底網！</span></strong></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>只要網上充斥住假嘅起底圖，而且難分真假，起底圖就自然冇參考價值！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></strong></span><br />\n<br />\n做法好簡單：<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">1. 喺藍屍 page 下載起底相</span></strong><br />\n__私人影嘅先做啦，炒報紙/<br />\n__直播嘅已經通晒天，無咩意思<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>2. 網上搵張相，人嘅角度同表情合適就得<br />\n</span></strong>__唔好用明星相就得<br />\n__用狗公狗乸圖效果更佳<ins></ins><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">3. 用 App 或者 PS key 個人樣上起底圖</strong></span><br />\n__推薦 app： Cupace<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>4. 用假帳號擺上另一個藍屍起底 page</strong></span><br />\n__唔好擺返落同一個 group，俾人認到<br />\n__唔洗介意俾佢哋發現係假圖。<br />\n__就係想佢哋見到張相都唔知真假。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/wjFoHT1.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FwjFoHT1.jpg&h=19766506&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n（呢張例圖我 hea 做嘅，表情唔合適。）<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">目的係令佢哋好似捉鬼咁捉假圖，啲圖就會失去公信力</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n啲圖唔知真假，好難呈堂<br />\n班狗跟住圖咬女義士，點知咬親阿嫂<br />\n藍屍想認樣打義士打唔到<br />\n咁我哋就成功喇！"},{"pid":"6f007fb92c7be6a6b8696dd854ec0bb4cbd8d04f","tid":1605110,"uid":236171,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-30T07:40:00.000Z","msg":"幫手推！招募易容師一齊做嘢！！"},{"pid":"ee6fffa335af3fc570975b0dc90d31e04dc30e8c","tid":1605110,"uid":299742,"like":11,"dislike":0,"score":11,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-09-30T07:45:24.000Z","msg":"學術上研究<br />\n係咪要證實相片真偽，需要當事人上庭作證？<br />\n咁如果太多改圖，點先分清邊張係真假？"},{"pid":"3ffe7c4d2f75ecbd018c7223b7431863c56fdbbc","tid":1605110,"uid":236171,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"ee6fffa335af3fc570975b0dc90d31e04dc30e8c","tid":1605110,"uid":299742,"like":11,"dislike":0,"score":11,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-09-30T07:45:24.000Z","msg":"學術上研究<br />\n係咪要證實相片真偽，需要當事人上庭作證？<br />\n咁如果太多改圖，點先分清邊張係真假？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-30T07:47:45.000Z","msg":"冇錯，我就係要呢啲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c67dbf1c46139d85c21414b097d015e29a93886b","tid":1605110,"uid":236171,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"quote":{"pid":"ee6fffa335af3fc570975b0dc90d31e04dc30e8c","tid":1605110,"uid":299742,"like":11,"dislike":0,"score":11,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-09-30T07:45:24.000Z","msg":"學術上研究<br />\n係咪要證實相片真偽，需要當事人上庭作證？<br />\n咁如果太多改圖，點先分清邊張係真假？"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-30T07:49:50.000Z","msg":"其實可以睇電話知道係影定改<br />\n問題係十假一真，都唔知搵邊個做證"},{"pid":"03840a9143e2fcbd8679ae6cb3b2abf6d00aa2ae","tid":1605110,"uid":236171,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-30T07:55:57.000Z","msg":"鍵盤戰士，除咗國際文宣之外仲可以做好多嘢架<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5326643d609c30219f45648aa0fac0f0d85799b3","tid":1605110,"uid":278180,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-30T08:00:37.000Z","msg":"強大！有用！"},{"pid":"e4b722ec495a9c3f86b5eb4b5c9476367ab3dea7","tid":1605110,"uid":236171,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-30T08:04:45.000Z","msg":"唔該幫手推上熱門!!"}